channel.title: How to get JDK for Vista?
channel.description: How do you get it for Vista? I'm trying to help my friend and I can't figure it out

item.title: How to get JDK for Vista?
item.dc:creator: @OrionScape OrionScape
item.description:
@OrionScape wrote:

Guys, when you install it, you have to select Windows x64 or something like that. x64 represents that you are using 64-bit software. My processor is x64, but I am running an x86 operating system. Go to se.java.com and install it again!
